name: Baxton_Studio_Agathe_Modern_Contemporary_Dark_Grey_Fabric_Upholstered_Headboard
reviews: This was a great price for this headboard. It could be a bit more sturdy. It was easy to attach to the bed frame. Would recommend this.
It is thin and it's a bit flimsy. But it looks so good. It's a great deal, specially for the price.
description: You can imagine this designer piece feeling right at home in a villa in the Hollywood Hills or a lavish loft in New York. Transform your space into a luxurious hideaway.  The beautiful nailhead detailing cornering the headboard adds that subtle sparkle that every glamorous bedroom dreams of!
